{"article_id":"eJ5ipHdPUqbon8lt","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Democrats continued to send mixed signals on impeachment Thursday ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"even as the House Judiciary Committee moved ahead with approving procedures for their investigation into President Trump .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"The committee voted 24-17 to implement four procedures ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"marking the first time","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"the panel voted on what Judiciary Democrats are calling an impeachment investigation .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"The rules would allow Chairman Jerrold Nadler , New York Democrat , to delegate some of the work to subcommittees ;","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"give committee staff extra time","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"to question witnesses ;","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"govern how information is kept private ;","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"and allow for President Trump ' s legal team to review and respond .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"The vote Thursday was not a question","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"of whether to impeachment the president ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"but merely lays out investigation rules","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"that would determine","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"whether Democrats should offer articles of impeachment .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Mr. Nadler has publicly said","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"his panel is conducting formal impeachment proceedings with this investigation ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"and attempted to brush aside the debate during Thursday ' s vote .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"\" Some call this process an impeachment inquiry ,","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"some call it an impeachment investigation .","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"There is no legal difference between these terms ,","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"and I no longer care to argue about the nomenclature , \"","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Judiciary Democrats have embraced that ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"this impeachment investigation has been going on for a while .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"Other Democrats have offered different descriptions","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"of what they thought","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"the committee was up to","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"- one member told The Times","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"it was crafting language","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"to start an impeachment inquiry .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"On Thursday , a handful of members took up the \" impeachment investigation \" term ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"including Rep. Hakeem Jeffries ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"who had avoided the \" i word \" just the day before .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi , however , is not wavering on her own messaging .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"\" Impeachment is a very divisive measure ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"but","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"if we have to go there ,","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"we ' ll go there .","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"But we can ' t go there","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"unless we have the facts , \"","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"Notably , she ' s avoided both explicitly shutting down the term \" impeachment investigation \" and using it herself .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Rather , she doubled down on the argument","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"she ' s been using for months","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"- impeachment is a possibility","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"but six committees first must finish their months-long investigations .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"\" I stand by what we have been doing all along .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"I support what is happening in the Judiciary Committee","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"because that enables them to do their process of interrogation and their investigation .","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"And I salute them for that work , \"","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"Mrs. Pelosi told reporters on Thursday .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"\" That ' s all","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"I ' m going to way on the subject ,","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"and there ' s nothing different from one day to the next , \"","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"she added .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"Republicans argue","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"the confusion and disarray from Democrats on impeachment is because they ' re circumventing the proper process .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Rep. Doug Collins of Georgia , the top Republican on the Judiciary Committee , has repeatedly pushed back on Mr. Nadler ' s claim","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"that the committee was working on formal impeachment proceedings ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"arguing","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"that they would need a full House vote","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"to authorize such an investigation .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"\" The difference between formal impeachment proceedings and what we ' re doing today is a world apart","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"no matter what the chairman just said , \"","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"Mr. Collins said .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"\" The ambiguity","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"- the confusion -","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"is a product of my colleagues ' own making","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"because there is an easy way","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"to know exactly","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"whether this committee is in impeachment proceedings :","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"it ' s called a vote","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"- a vote of the full House of Representatives , \"","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"he added .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"At the GOP retreat in Baltimore on Thursday afternoon , both Mr. Collins and Rep. Jim Jordan of Ohio called this latest impeachment push a desperate play for Democrats .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"\" The reason","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"they want to do this ...","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"the reason","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"they want to change the rules","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"is because nothing else has worked for them , \"","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Mr. Jordan said .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"Minority Leader Kevin McCarthy said","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"the Democrats ' mixed messaging on impeachment is proof","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"Mrs. Pelosi is struggling to maintain control of her party .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"\" She has the title","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"but no longer the power","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"to manage the floor , \"","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"\" You can ' t even understand what they ' re doing in committee ,","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"especially when it comes to Chairman Nadler . \"","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"The top House Republican said","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"he is confident","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"that the Democrats ' work on investigating Mr. Trump","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"will be a boon for GOP House candidates in 2020 .","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"He pointed out","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"that Republicans only need to flip 18 seats","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"to retake the majority","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"- fewer than the Democrats needed","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"going into the 2018 election -","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"and there are 31 Democrats in vulnerable districts","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"the president carried in 2016 .","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"\" Tell me , how are Democrats going to go back and ask for reelection","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"on what they have achieved .","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"All","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"they have achieved","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"is investigations","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"that have gone nowhere , \"","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"Mr. McCarthy said .","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"Free Speech For People , By the People , CREDO Action , Courage Campaign , Democracy For America , Mainers for Responsible Leadership , and March for Truth are demanding","depth":4},{"id":111,"text":"the committee vote on articles of impeachment by Nov. 1 and a full House vote by Nov. 15 .","depth":4},{"id":112,"text":"Some Judiciary members have floated the possibility","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"of reaching a decision","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"on whether or not to move forward with articles of impeachment by the end of the year ,","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"but haven ' t committed to any firm date .","depth":5},{"id":116,"text":"\" We will not allow Congress to run out the clock on impeachment , \"","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"read a joint statement from the activists .","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"\" Congress has now had the Mueller Report","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"- only one data point in a comprehensive case for Trump ' s impeachment -","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"for more than four months .","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"Our democracy , our communities","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"that are under attack ,","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"and our planet can not wait any longer","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"for Congress to lead . \"","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"For his part , Mr. Nadler plans to hit the ground running with more hearings .","depth":3},{"id":126,"text":"\" With these new procedures , we will begin next week an aggressive series of hearings","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"investigating allegations of corruption , obstruction and abuse of power against the president , \"","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"he said after the Judiciary meeting .","depth":6},{"id":129,"text":"\" The investigation go well beyond the four corners of the Mueller report . \"","depth":5},{"id":130,"text":"The Judiciary Committee is also looking into potential corruption ,","depth":5},{"id":131,"text":"launching probes into Vice President Mike Pence ' s stay at a Trump-owned property in Ireland and the president ' s effort","depth":6},{"id":132,"text":"to host the Group of Seven summit at one of his Miami golf resorts .","depth":6},{"id":133,"text":"The first hearing under the new rules will be on Sept. 17","depth":3},{"id":134,"text":"featuring former Trump campaign manager Corey Lewandowski .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":269,"left":259,"right":268,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":244,"right":258,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":166,"right":243,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":144,"right":165,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":136,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":138,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":2,"right":137,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":5,"right":141,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":141,"left":139,"right":140,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":139,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":165,"left":148,"right":164,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":145,"right":147,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":145,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":12,"right":146,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":164,"left":158,"right":163,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":158,"left":155,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":150,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclear